<white>synopsys:</>
    the command <green>groupadd</> is used to create a new group in the
    current website.

<white>usage: </><green>groupadd</> <yellow>$groupname</>

<white>important:</>
    <red>!</> this command will work only in a website context. for 
    choosing a website context, see the <green>use</> command.

<white>arguments:</>
    <yellow>$groupname</> - the name of the group. it is recommended to 
         use only lowercase letters, as the group names are case 
         sensitive.

<white>examples:</>
    <green>groupadd</> <yellow>users</>
        will add a group <yellow>users</> in the current website.